# ALIEN TAKE DOWN

## Description
This is a video web-based game battling aliens to save planet earth. Several alien ships come to earth to take it. You are the USSAssembly ship and you must attack each alien ship that comes down to attack earth using your attack button. All ships have firepower, hull or life points, and accuracy of aim. After you attack the alien ships, the alien ships will attack back. You will have th option to retreat at any point in time, but you will lose the game if you don't attack. Good Luck! 